<span style="color: #ffffff">You don't.</span>
<br />
<span style="color: #ffffff">Not you personally. Another will. You have something more important to attend to, remember?</span>
<br />
<span style="color: #b536da">TT: Oh, right.</span>
<br />
<span style="color: #b536da">TT: The Green...</span>
<br />
<span style="color: #b536da">TT: Wait.</span>
<br />
<span style="color: #b536da">TT: The <img src="http://www.mspaintadventures.com/storyfiles/hs2/scraps/greensun.gif" border="0" />.</span>
