<span style="color: #ffffff">Your needles won't suffice.</span>
<br />
<span style="color: #b536da">TT: Then where do I get ones that will?</span>
<br />
<span style="color: #ffffff">Again, you won't. This task is out of your hands.</span>
<br />
<span style="color: #ffffff">The needles must be acquired from the denizen of the Witch of Space.</span>
<br />
<span style="color: #ffffff">Her quills are very large and potent. They will be able to cause the Scratch.</span>
